Paragliding in Carmona.

Do something different and enjoyable, try paragliding. 

✅ View&#39;s Schedule: 
Mon - Sun: 5:00am - 10:00pm

✅ Entrance and Paragliding Fee: 
Php10.00/head
Php2,000/overnight
Php300.00/Photoshoot
Php300.00/Cottage
Php100.00/Tent (If one wish to set up a tent)
Php3,500.00/Paragliding for 15 mins.

✅ ACCESSIBILITY: Accessible to all types of transportation. 

✅ PARKING AREA: There is an allotted parking area before the entrance of Airkin&#39;s view.

✅ ADDRESS:  Barangay Lantic, Carmona, Cavite 

✅ Follow and like Visit Cavite

✳️ Pictures are owned by Visit Cavite. No pictures can be used or reproduced without the approval of the owner of the Visit Cavite page.

