Enjoy a good view at this place in Silang. You can either take the Tagaytay-Sta. Road or Emilio Aguinaldo Highway.

✅ Farm Schedule: 
Mon - Sun: 8:00am - 8:00pm

✅ Entrance Fee: Php100.00
If you will dine in at the restaurant, you need not pay the entrance fee

✅ ACCESSIBILITY: Accessible to private transportation.

✅ PARKING AREA: With parking space 

✅ ADDRESS:  9755 Purok 5, Barangay Pulong Bunga, Silang, Cavite

